<h1><u>Dogs:</u> <i>Man's Best Friend!</i></h1>

<p>The dog is a pet animal. A dog has <b>sharp teeth</b> so that it can eat flesh very easily, it has <i>four legs</i>, two ears, two eyes, a tail, a mouth, and a nose. <b>It is a very clever animal and is very useful in catching thieves.</b> It runs very fast, barks loudly and attacks the strangers. A dog saves the life of the master from danger. <br><br>One can find dogs everywhere in the world. Dogs are a very faithful animal. It has a sharp mind and a strong sense of hearing smelling the things. It also has many qualities like swimming in the water, jumping from anywhere, good smelling sense.
</p>

<h2>Importance Of a Dog</h2>
<p>A dog has a strong power of smell. They are more liked by people because of their faithfulness. They are intelligent, they are watchfulness. The dogs have many colors such as grey, white, black, brown and red.</p>
<p>The dogs are so loyal to his master that nothing can induce him to leave his master. His master might be a poor man or even a beggar but still, the dog will not leave his master from far off. Dogs see their master coming home from work they rush to them and jump on them to show their love. Dogs are honest friends who are always ready to die to save a friend. It can bite a thief or stranger when they ignore its barking and try to mischief. Dogs always give security to the owner day and night.</p>

